Single cell RNA-seq datasets

rm(list = ls())
load(file = "./scRNAseq/Melanoma_ssGSEA_res_longdf.Rdata")
Score_long_df %>%
  filter(pathways == "CD73_pathway") %>% filter(cellType != "Unknow") -> CD73s
p <- ggboxplot(CD73s, x = "cellType", y = "score", palette = "jco",color = "cellType",
          add = "jitter") + 
  # stat_compare_means() +
  geom_hline(yintercept = mean(CD73s$score), linetype = 2) +
  stat_compare_means(label = "p.signif",
                     ref.group = ".all.", hide.ns = TRUE)  +    # Pairwise comparison against all
  theme(legend.position = "none") +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1, color = "black"),
        axis.text.y = element_text(size = 8,color = "black")) +
  labs(x = "", y = "ssGSEA score (CD73s)") +ggtitle("GSE72056 Melanoma")
p

rm(list = ls())
load(file = "./scRNAseq/HNSC_ssGSEA_res_longdf.Rdata")
Score_long_df %>%
  filter(pathways == "CD73_pathway") -> CD73s
p <- ggboxplot(CD73s, x = "cell_type", y = "score", palette = "jco",color = "cell_type",
          add = "jitter") + 
  # stat_compare_means() +
  geom_hline(yintercept = mean(CD73s$score), linetype = 2) +
  stat_compare_means(label = "p.signif",
                     ref.group = ".all.", hide.ns = TRUE)   +   # Pairwise comparison against all
  theme(legend.position = "none") +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1, color = "black"),
        axis.text.y = element_text(size = 8,color = "black"))  + 
  labs(x = "", y = "ssGSEA score (CD73s)") +ggtitle("GSE103322 HNSCC")
p
